# RegenerateAccessKeyParameters

Parameters supplied to the regenerate authorization rule operation, specifies which key neeeds to be reset.

## Properties

Name | Type | Description | Notes
------------ | ------------- | ------------- | -------------
**key** | **str** | Optional. If the key value is provided, this is set to key type, or autogenerated key value set for key type. | [optional] 
**key_type** | **str** | The access key to regenerate. |
